"Skibidi Toilet India" is a third-person shooter game inspired by the YouTube content creator DaFuq!?Boom!'s series skibidi toilet. In this game, you have to eliminate an army of walking toilets. To accomplish this task, you will have access to a variety of weapons. Additionally, there is a titan boss in the game who is the leader of the toilet army, and you must defeat him to win the game. So, get ready with your weapons!
